high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the stove.
Pick up the kettle on the right side of the stove.
Turn around and walk over to the sink.
Put the kettle in the sink and turn on the faucet then turn the faucet off. Pick up the kettle.
Turn around and walk to the brown shelves near the kitchen counter.
Put the kettle on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleanly washed kettle on the second shelf in the kitchen.

high_descs: Turn left and go pass the table towards the stove
Take the kettle on the right
Turn around and go to the sink on your left
Put the kettle in the sink, turn on the faucet and wash the kettle with water
Take the kettle and turn around and walk to the end of the room
Put the kettle on the second shelf from the bottom
anns.task_desc: Take the kettle from the stove ,wash it,  put it on the shelf in the corner

high_descs: Turn left and walk around the left side of the center table and turn left to face the stove.
Pick up the tea pot on the front right burner.
Turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Wash the tea pot in the sink, then pick it back up.
Turn around, walk across the room and turn to the right to face the shelves.
Place the tea pot on the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: To clean a tea pot and store it on the second shelf from the bottom on the wall.

high_descs: Go left and then right and then turn to the left to face the stove.
Pick the tea pot on the bottom right of the stove up.
Turn to the right and face the stove.
Put the tea pot in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then pick the tea pot up again.
Turn around and cross the room and turn to face the brown shelves.
Put the tea pot on the shelf that is second from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tea pot on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the stove.
Pick up the kettle on the right.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink.
Turn around and walk past the counter to the shelving on the right.
Place the kettle on the right side of the shelf closest to the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean kettle on a shelf.
